data.description: Check out this cute home in a great location in North Nampa! Darling Open floor plan with vaulted ceilings. LVP flooring in the main areas. 3 bedroom plus a den with french doors. The den has a closet so it could be a 4 th bedroom.   Split bedroom floor plan. The kitchen features a breakfast bar, dishwasher, oven and pantry. The master suite has his and her closets, tile bathroom floor and tile surround in the tub/shower.  Brand new a/c unit this year.  Gas Furnace 2016. Gas Hot Water Heater new within last few years.  Solar panels included.   Roof is approximately 8 years old.  Spacious fully fenced backyard with a storage shed and a fire pit.  RV parking on the side of the home.  Conveniently located to freeway access, shopping and so much more.
